&lt;h2 id=&quot;gear&quot;&gt;Gear&lt;a role=&quot;anchor&quot; aria-hidden tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; data-no-popover href=&quot;#gear&quot; class=&quot;internal&quot;&gt;&lt;svg width=&quot;18&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 24 24&quot; fill=&quot;none&quot; stroke=&quot;currentColor&quot; stroke-width=&quot;2&quot; stroke-linecap=&quot;round&quot; stroke-linejoin=&quot;round&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Impeccably dressed in brand-name clothes. &lt;mark style=&quot;background: #BBFABBA6;&quot;&gt;Black leather gloves&lt;/mark&gt;. Expensive coat. Robust winter shoes, as you will go into desolate houses and Zug Island. &lt;mark style=&quot;background: #BBFABBA6;&quot;&gt;Portfolio with a laptop&lt;/mark&gt; and important documents. Smartphone of the latest model. &lt;mark style=&quot;background: #BBFABBA6;&quot;&gt;Small video camera to film Franklin&lt;/mark&gt;, if needed. Keys. Wallet with various credit cards and a few business cards. Antibacterial tissue in your pocket.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paczka papierosów z lat 70. (prawie pełna bez jednego papierosa).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
